    18→ *  • A dedicated ingestion thread continuously pulls data from the LMS.
    19→ *  • A monitor thread subscribes to Observer events (e.g., drift detected).
    20→ *  • Mutex-protected state keeps the pipeline life-cycle thread-safe.
