     8→ *   • Wiring up Observer hooks
     9→ *   • Spawning background schedulers (model-drift detection, retraining)
    10→ *   • Executing the high-level controller pipeline
    11→ *   • Graceful shutdown on POSIX signals
    12→ *
    13→ * The file is self-contained so that it can be compiled standalone for demo /
    14→ * PoC purposes.  In the real project these helper structs live in dedicated
    15→ * translation units.
    16→ */
