| | `pipeline_manager.h/.c` | Pipeline orchestration |
| | `drift_detector.h/.c` | Drift detection logic |
| | `model_monitor.h/.c` | Performance surveillance |
| | `retraining_trigger.h/.c` | Retraining policy |
| | `observer.h` | Observer Pattern infrastructure |
| | `job_factory.h/.c` | Factory Pattern for jobs |
| | `task_scheduler.h/.c` | Task execution engine |

